Managing guest access over time is essential to maintaining security when external users collaborate with an organization.

Microsoft Entra ID provides lifecycle management capabilities such as:

* Access reviews
* Expiration policies
* Guest user removal
* Conditional Access for guests

For example, a consultant invited for a 3-month project can automatically lose access after project completion.

A real-life use case is enterprises working with temporary contractors or vendors.

Another example is universities granting temporary access to visiting researchers.

Managing guest access over time prevents unnecessary permissions, reduces security risk, and supports governance.
